{"tid":1560434,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"愛香港, 愛香港國歌嘅同我入嚟！","createTime":"2019-09-11T07:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T08:04:09.000Z","uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5f7f320985141c7c72b13d933a057eb2c1172da2","tid":1560434,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:50:16.000Z","msg":"我相信大家都已經聽過香港國歌，作曲嘅人簡直係一流！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係我想建議一下大家首歌唔好finalize住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為我有少少建議，<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 第一我想我哋嘅國歌有中英語在裏面，就好似南非嘅國歌一樣，裏面有五種語言。 香港國歌有兩種語言，有幾個原因第一，我想強調<br />\n 1.1, 香港系一個國際嘅城市，係全世界其中一個最特別嘅地方，所以我哋嘅國歌有兩種語言組成係不足為奇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 1.2, 第二，香港係英國曾經嘅殖民地，我想強調呢一個歷史，<br />\n 1.3, 尤其我哋希望得到國際認同，英語有助我哋表達，<br />\n 1.4, 我要話比大陸狗聽，你哋唔使旨意追得到我哋香港！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我哋嘅獨特性，你成世都唔會有！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2, 等二，可能可以多一點簡單音易懂的字？我有啲好有心的朋友，但說記吾到，因為有少少橋口。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總括嚟講，我好鍾意首國歌，希望令佢完美！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f30d0d5876c8f91726e4e944f762afe999869494","tid":1560434,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:52:17.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"8f22f9b0216d6ba00a6807c1e48784e2ac19d01b","tid":1560434,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:52:48.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"f178a53b1241b54e8877f4a03ae3af8134510022","tid":1560434,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5367dd662a915efae0610164780d6e96d6ea2b38","tid":1560434,"uid":273466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT